1ja n 8ja n 15ja n 22ja n 29feb 5feb 12feb 19 ja n 1ja n 8ja n 15ja n 22ja n 29feb 5fe b 12fe b 19any experienced manager will agree that business manage ment is subject of how to get results company listing important note the people listed in this directory are all members of wise and have signed an agreement committing themselves to standardly applying lrh admin tech in their business activities and to upholding the code of wise member if you encounter any nonoptimum situation in dealing with anyone listed in this directory please report it to the wise reports officer of your nearest wise office so it can be addressed other businesspeople claiming to use lrh admin tech in their businesses who are not wise members have not signed an agreement with wise to honor such commitments if as wise member you suspect or find that someone is using this directory or any part of it as mailing list immediately report your observation to the wise reports officer of your nearest wise office with copy of the report to the wise reports officer at wise international the listings in the wise directory are the property of wise international only and may not be used by others people listed in this directory are all members of wise and have signed an agreement committing themselves to standardly applying lrh admin tech in their business activities and to upholding the code of wise member if you encounter any nonoptimum situation in dealing with anyone listed in this directory please report it to the wise reports officer of your nearest wise office so it can be addressed other businesspeople claiming to use lrh admin tech in their businesses who are not wise members have not signed an agreement with wise to honor such commitments if as wise member you suspect or find that someone is using this directory or any part of it as mailing list immediately report your observation to the wise reports officer of your nearest wise office with copy of the report to the wise reports officer at wise international the listings in the wise directory are the property of wise international only and may not be used by others without prior written authorization the only approved 300wise international directory 200 6 how to advertise in the wise directory wise membership is an opportunity to meet and form relationships with likeminded professionals of all walks of life and not just in your community to help you form such relationships we provide the wise international business directory available to all members each receives copy and is listed the wise international business directory includes alphabetical listings as well as listings by geographical area and business category each wise member may provide concise description of hisher business or activity to include in the listing wise members may also purchase advertising space this publication also includes listings of groups within the wise membership including charter committees and business expansion clubs how can i be listed in the wise directory when you sign up as wise member you fill out wise membership registration form the contact information and description of your business which you provide is sent to our directory database incharge and is used to create your wise directory listing if your contact information or business description changes at any time simply send the updated information to the directory database ic wise international with copy to your nearest wise office on page 303 there is form showing the information which is used to compile your directory listing if for some reason you do not wish to be listed in the wise directory then inform the directory database ic wise international as members are listed automatically upon verification at wise international there are specific requirements for being listed in the wise directory other than that one is current member of wise abiding by the code of wise member and operating an ethical business the member ethics officer at wise international reviews the final listings to ensure those included are actually abiding by the code of wise member with ones ethics in per the information available to him can the wise directory be used as mailing list the wise directory cannot be used as mailing list without specific permission from wise international our members provide their contact information in good faith and in general welcome communication from fellow members however when these communication lines are overloaded with unsolicited offerings this can undermine the wise directory as membership benefit at wise international we work to safeguard the communication lines of our members however we are equally interested in keeping these lines free and open the solution is to advertise in the wise directory this is without doubt the most cost effective way to reach wise members with an ad all year long how can one advertise in the wise directory variety of advertising spaces are available to members if you would like to advertise please use the form on page 302 198762006 wise directory 132300304indd 300 71906 84122 pm directory listingsinternational business directory 2006wise wise international business directory wise onlinedirectory listingswise international business directory wise online301wise international directory 200 6 directory advertising policy acceptance of all advertising is subject to publishers approval and agreement by the advertiser to indemnify and protect the publisher from loss or expense on claim or suits based upon contents of the subject matter of such advertisement this includes suits for libel plagiarism copyright infringement and unauthorized use of persons name or photograph among others cancellation is not accepted after applicable closing date the publisher reserves the right to reject or cancel any advertisement which in his opinion does not conform to the standards of the publication the publisher shall not be liable for damages if for any reason he fails to publish an advertisement the publisher assumes liability for errors or omissions of key numbers or for the content of an advertisement or listing all advertising shall be clearly identified with trademark or signature of advertisers conversion and any unusual production charges related to advertising material are billed at prevailing rates advertising materials are returned upon request only otherwise all material is retained twelve months and then destroyed unless being reused in future directories publisher shall not be bound by any conditions printed or otherwise appearing on order blanks or copy instructions which conflict with the provisions of these policies and the ad specifications publisher reserves the right to cancel contract upon default in payment of unpaid charges by the advertiser publisher reserves the right to give better position than specified at increase in rate what format does my ad need to be in our advertisement needs to be in format which is macintosh compatible it should be sent as an electronic file including any artwork and fonts and as printout to the directory ic wise international via the registration chief of your nearest wise office what are the costs and sizes of advertisements there are five available sizes for advertisements full page color 7 12 x 9 14 150000 full page bw 6 12 x 8 18 11000012 page bw 6 12 x 4 116 65000 13 page bw 6 12 x 2 34 50000 14 page bw 6 12 x 2 37500 16 page bw 6 12 x 1 14 25000 these ads can be horizontal or vertical how to get listed in the wise directory to get listed in the wise directory please fill out the form on page 303 all listing information advertisements and payments must be received by 1 november each year to be included in the next years directory listingswise international business directory wise onlineimportant note the people listed in this directory are all members of wise and have signed an agreement committing themselves to standardly applying lrh admin tech in their business activities and to upholding the code of wise member if you encounter any nonoptimum situation in dealing with anyone listed in this directory please report it to the wise reports officer of your nearest wise office so it can be addressed if as wise member you suspect or find that someone is using this directory or any part of it as mailing list immediately report your observa tion to the wise reports officer of your nearest wise office with copy of the report to the wise reports officer at wise international the listings in the wise directory are the property of wise international only and may not be used by others without prior written authorization the only approved line to promote to wise members is through an advertisement in the wise
